      • classHash

        protected byte[] classHash
        Memoizes a secure hash of the class. If this class-type information is derived from a FabIL or Fabric signature, this field holds a hash of the signature source. If the class-type information is derived from a source file, this field holds a hash of that source file. Otherwise, the class-type information is derived from a Java class file, and this field holds a hash of that class's bytecode.
